00:55.920 --> 00:57.900
Yeah, well, it's also
a holiday weekend,

00:58.000 --> 01:01.030
so will you please just call it
a tropical storm, please?

01:01.130 --> 01:03.120
I love this town.
They even spin the weather.

01:03.220 --> 01:06.240
All right, listen. We gotta go live
on this one, so don't screw it up.

01:06.340 --> 01:09.370
And Al, I think that's Powell going
in there with Secretary Kirkland.

01:09.470 --> 01:11.460
Zoom in on them during the intro.

01:11.560 --> 01:13.370
Anyway, why can't I
do this from inside?

01:13.470 --> 01:14.590
All right, we're rolling.

01:14.690 --> 01:16.010
Why do I have to stand
out here like a...

01:16.110 --> 01:16.670
Five, four, three,

